h4. Actor:
Administrator.

h4. Description:
Name of use case represents its functionality.

h4. Flow:
* Actor clicks [Settings|guide:_ShowApplicationPlugin] option from top menu bar.
* "Settings" sub menu of left menu should show as default.
* Click *Employee* link.
* [Show Landing Page of Employee|guide:ShowEmployeeActionService].
* Select a Line-Item from grid view.
* Click "Edit" button from tool bar.
* Open *Employee* in Edit Mode.

h4. Pre-condition:
* User must have "Select Employee" privilege.

h4. Process:
* Get *Employee* details from server.

h4. Post-condition:

* *Success:*
** Show selected *Employee* information in input form.

* *Failure:*
** Show error message for details visit [Error Handler|common Usecases].
